taken evil counsel against thee, saying,","year":-741},{"id":"recnZHCgANEY3ndA1","ref":"Isa.7.6","text":"Let us go up against Judah, and vex it, and let us make a breach therein for us, and set a king in the midst of it, even the son of Tabeal:","year":-741},{"id":"recbdacnCE0cLEcBV","ref":"Isa.7.7","text":"Thus saith the Lord GOD, It shall not stand, neither shall it come to pass.","year":-741},{"id":"recIiwY36C8aW0NIp","ref":"Isa.7.8","text":"For the head of Syria is Damascus, and the head of Damascus is Rezin; and within threescore and five years shall Ephraim be broken, that it be not a people.","year":-741}]}
